Package pkgMain

Class Recommendation

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.Recommendation
public class Recommendation
extends java.lang.Object
Displays the recommended plants based on previous user inputs. User can add these plants to that basket to be used in the garden. Hovering over a plant shows information about each plant and lep combo.
Author:
Matthew
